data.description: Check out this BEAUTIFUL colonial situated in the heart of SCS! This 1800 square foot home has been completely renovated from top to bottom in 2018! This home features a totally open floor plan, vinyl floors throughout, and beautiful kitchen with custom shaker cabinets, quartz counters, custom back splash, HUGE 8 foot island AND a walk in pantry! Cozy living room with gas fireplace, ship lap wall, and sliding door wall off the back of the home that leads out to your 18 ft deck, perfect for entertaining! Separate dining space off the living room. Den/Office in the front of the home and custom half bath finish off the first floor! Head upstairs to your new Master bedroom with walk in closet AND walk-in waterfall shower with custom tile! Two other good sized bedrooms with double closets! SECOND FLOOR LAUNDRY ROOM! Fenced backyard and 2.5 car garage with electricity and extra long driveway. Unfinished basement for all your storage needs. All updates within the last 5 years include; Plumbing, electrical, tank less water heater, furnace, AC, roof and windows! This home is totally move-in ready and offer immediate occupancy!
